{"tid":1056083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［又周街斬人？］葵涌男子街頭遇襲　手腳中刀受傷","createTime":"2019-03-11T02:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T02:49:35.000Z","uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"873141b68304c76ca020bd969a2e0b0bb570be34","tid":1056083,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T02:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今早(11日)9時許，一名男子途經葵涌葵定路11號街頭時，遭一名持刀男子襲擊，他走避不及擋格時手腳中刀，途人目睹大驚報警，刀手逞兇後逃去。 <br />\n<br />\n多輛衝鋒警車趕至，事主中刀仍然清醒，經包紮後由救護車送院急救，警員在場向途人了解，並於附近兜截疑人，暫未有發現。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190311/photo/bkn-20190311101119487-0311_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190311103044\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190311%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190311101119487-0311_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190311103044&h=32c25d50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190311/mobile/bkn-20190311101119487-0311_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190311%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190311101119487-0311_00822_001.html&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FJS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=3b1ba9be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190311/mobile/bkn-20190311101119487-0311_00822_001.html</a>"}]}